abla=I-E^{-1}\) \(\delta=E^{1 / 2}-E^{-1 / 2}\) 差分与差商的关系： \(f\left[x_{0}, x_{1}ight]= rac{f\left(x_{1}ight)-f\left(x_{0}ight)}{x_{1}-x_{0}}= rac{\Delta f\left(x_{0}ight)}{1 \cdot h}\) 插值公式 向前： \(N_{n}(a+t h)=f\left(x_{0}ight)+\sum_{k=1}^{n}  rac{\Delta^{k} f\left(x_{0}ight)}{k !} t(t-1) \cdots(t-k+1)\) \(N_{2}\left(x_{0}+t hight)=f\left(x_{0}ight)+ rac{\Delta f\left(x_{0}ight)}{1 !} t+ rac{\Delta^{2} f\left(x_{0}ight)}{2 !} t(t-1)\) 向后： \(N_{n}(b+t h)=f\left(x_{n}ight)+\sum_{k=1}^{n}  rac{
abla^{k} f\left(x_{n}ight)}{k !} t(t+1) \cdots(t+k-1)\) Hermite插值 插值条件 \(\left\{ egin{array}{l}{H_{2 n+1}\left(x_{i}ight)=f\left(x_{i}ight)} \ {H_{2 n+1}^{\prime}\left(x_{i}ight)=f^{\prime}\left(x_{i}ight)}\end{array} i=0,1,2, \cdots, night. （唯一性）\) 插值基 插值多项式 余项
